    private static class Algebra.ExcludeReadingGraphsVisitor.ExcludeReadingGraphsVisitor1
extends org.openrdf.query.algebra.helpers.QueryModelVisitorBase<RuntimeException>
    Helper class supporting the rewriting of TupleExpr so to prevent reading from graphs whose URIs match a certain prefix.

    NOTE: this class is not thread safe.
